name: Diamond in the Rough
description:
Feedback, Cameras, CRTs, Oh MY!
A clip I long dreamed of getting perfect.
It took me a while to figure out that it was my concept of perfect that was flawed.
Fortunately Janus was around to tell me it was good enough, but I still didnt listen.
After many months of tinkering with it, and a few months of leaving it alone, I was able to approach it fresh and settle on this iteration of things.
